descriptions.description: This dataset shows the Battery Electric Vehicles (BEVs) and Plug-in Hybrid Electric Vehicles (PHEVs) that are currently registered through Washington State         Department of Licensing (DOL).

descriptions.tableofcontents: VIN -- County -- City -- State -- Postal Code -- Model Year -- Make -- Model -- Electric Vehicle Type -- Clean Alternative Fuel Vehicle (CAFV) Eligibility -- Electric Range -- Base MSRP -- Legislative District -- DOL Vehicle ID -- Vehicle Location -- Electric Utility -- 2020 Census Tract
